<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mill" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mill,</orth> a building in which corn is ground to meal: <cit><quote>more sacks to the m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.81" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 81</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>more water glideth by the m. than wots the miller of,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 85</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.309" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 309</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.10.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 10, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 18</bibl>.
